{"id":108818,"type":2,"name":"人魚","image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/m/77/a3/108818_nAIID.jpg","rating":{"total":30,"count":{"1":1,"2":0,"3":1,"4":2,"5":3,"6":11,"7":7,"8":3,"9":2,"10":0},"score":6.1},"summary":"遥远的国度里有个爱做梦的男孩。一天，他把一条从水塘中捉到的鱼儿幻想成了美人鱼，并为自己编造了一个美丽的童话故事。后来，男孩把“美人鱼”带回家放进鱼缸指给父母看，父母异常恐慌，因为该国度禁止人们做白日梦。 \r\n　　紧接，男孩迎来被警察盘问、医生治疗的日子，但他脑子里依旧挥不去美人鱼的身影，不过慢慢地，他的记忆开始模糊。治疗有了效果之后，男孩被释放回家，看见鱼缸里游着的真是别人所说的一条普通的鱼儿时，他非常伤心，手捧鱼儿来到最初发现“美人鱼”的水塘。","info":"<li><span>中文名: </span>人鱼</li><li><span>话数: </span>1</li><li><span>导演: </span><a href=\"/person/1318\" rel=\"v:directedBy\">手塚治虫</a></li><li><span>脚本: </span><a href=\"/person/1318\">手塚治虫</a></li><li><span>分镜: </span><a href=\"/person/1318\">手塚治虫</a></li><li><span>原画: </span><a href=\"/person/1318\">手塚治虫</a></li><li><span>动画制作: </span><a href=\"/person/2959\">虫プロダクション</a></li><li><span>别名: </span>Mermaid</li><li><span style=\"visibility:hidden;\">别名: </span>Ningyo</li><li><span>上映年度: </span>1964</li><li><span>片长: </span>8 min</li><li><span>IMDb链接: </span>tt0058342</li>","collection":{"wish":12,"collect":44,"on_hold":1,"dropped":2},"tags":[{"name":"短片","count":23},{"name":"1964","count":9},{"name":"手塚治虫","count":9},{"name":"原创","count":6},{"name":"虫Production","count":4},{"name":"日本动画","count":3},{"name":"剧场版","count":2},{"name":"虫制作","count":2},{"name":"实验","count":1},{"name":"线条+色块","count":1},{"name":"这TMD是艺术！","count":1},{"name":"洗脑治疗","count":1},{"name":"独立剧场版","count":1},{"name":"默剧","count":1},{"name":"泡面番","count":1},{"name":"OVA","count":1},{"name":"人鱼","count":1},{"name":"手冢治虫","count":1},{"name":"脑补","count":1},{"name":"60年代","count":1},{"name":"虫プロダクション","count":1}],"eps":[{"id":890251,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/890251","type":0,"sort":1,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"}],"staff":[{"id":1318,"image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/76/cf/1318_prsn_anidb.jpg","name":"手冢治虫","desc":"导演"},{"id":2959,"image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/77/9e/2959_prsn_anidb.jpg","name":"虫Production",